INPUT INSTRUCTIONS

  DATA:
  FILE = dat_pa.dat;

  VARIABLE:
  NAMES   = id day N C s m1-m20;
  CLUSTER = id;
  USEVAR  = N C y1-y20;
  BETWEEN = N C;
  MISSING = .;
  LAGGED  = y20(1);

  DEFINE:
  CENTER N C (GRANDMEAN);
  y1 = m1 / 10;
  y2 = m2 / 10;
  y3 = m3 / 10;
  y4 = m4 / 10;
  y5 = m5 / 10;
  y6 = m6 / 10;
  y7 = m7 / 10;
  y8 = m8 / 10;
  y9 = m9 / 10;
  y10 = m10 / 10;
  y11 = m11 / 10;
  y12 = m12 / 10;
  y13 = m13 / 10;
  y14 = m14 / 10;
  y15 = m15 / 10;
  y16 = m16 / 10;
  y17 = m17 / 10;
  y18 = m18 / 10;
  y19 = m19 / 10;
  y20 = m20 / 10;

  ANALYSIS:
  TYPE = TWOLEVEL RANDOM;
  ESTIMATOR = BAYES;
  PROC = 8;
  FBITER = 50000;
  BSEED = 1213;

  MODEL:
  %WITHIN%
  resvar_1 | y1;
  resvar2-resvar20 | y2-y20;

  day_ar1 | y2 ON y1;
  day_ar2 | y3 ON y2;
  day_ar3 | y4 ON y3;
  day_ar4 | y5 ON y4;
  day_ar5 | y6 ON y5;
  day_ar6 | y7 ON y6;
  day_ar7 | y8 ON y7;
  day_ar8 | y9 ON y8;
  day_ar9 | y10 ON y9;
  day_ar10 | y11 ON y10;
  day_ar11 | y12 ON y11;
  day_ar12 | y13 ON y12;
  day_ar13 | y14 ON y13;
  day_ar14 | y15 ON y14;
  day_ar15 | y16 ON y15;
  day_ar16 | y17 ON y16;
  day_ar17 | y18 ON y17;
  day_ar18 | y19 ON y18;
  day_ar19 | y20 ON y19;

  night_ar | y1 ON y20&1;

  %BETWEEN%
  mu BY y1-y20@1;
  mu;
  [mu];
  [y1-y20@0];
  y1-y20@0;

  day_ar by day_ar1-day_ar19@1;
  day_ar*0.01;
  [day_ar*0.6](phi);
  [day_ar1-day_ar19@0];
  day_ar1-day_ar19@0;

  night_ar*0.01;
  [night_ar*0.15](alpha);

  resvar BY resvar2-resvar20@1;
  resvar;
  [resvar];
  resvar2-resvar20@0;
  [resvar2-resvar20@0];

  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar WITH
    mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar;

  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar ON N;
  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar ON C;
  C;

  MODEL CONSTRAINT:
  NEW(diff_ar);
  diff_ar = phi - alpha;

  OUTPUT:
  TECH1 TECH8 STDYX FSCOMPARISON STAND(CLUSTER);

  PLOT:
  TYPE = PLOT3;
  FACTOR = ALL (500);

  SAVEDATA:
  FILE IS pa_ar_difference.dat;
  SAVE IS FSCORES (500);
